entries.meaning: (obsolete) The art or means of characterizing; a system of signs or characters; symbolism; distinctive mark.
examples: When I have fears that I may cease to beBefore my pen has glean'd my teeming brain,Before high piled books, in charact'ry,Hold like rich garners the full ripen'd grain;

entries.meaning: (obsolete) That which is charactered; the meaning.
